0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T07:29:59.000Z","msg":"個肥婆 我屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaeb5013b0977cc653ca4ed27441cf8ef40a7df9","tid":227352,"uid":107983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T07:33:40.000Z","msg":"大部份肥到成座山咁嘅肥婆，條頸後面都好多老泥，因為佢哋沖涼嘅時候卒唔到。&nbsp;<br />\n老泥俾頸部脂肪一層層夾住，日復日年復年咁累積。&nbsp;<br />\n所以大部份肥婆條頸都係黑色，越黑老泥越厚。&nbsp;<br />\n如果你哋有幸溝到肥婆，就人一世物一世點都要試下。<br />\n首先用手指濕少少水起勢咁卒，用匙羹刮出嚟，加兩滴美極慢慢品嚐。&nbsp;<br />\n初哥可能話核突，但你唔食肥婆老泥等於登上白雲山唔食山水豆腐花一樣咁傻的嗎。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n下身方面又係有學問，肥婆食咁多漢堡包同牛肉，男性荷爾蒙分泌過盛。&nbsp;<br />\n所以塊西至屎o全部都係毛，無論佢幾乾淨，都有陣咸魚溝變壞乳酪嘅味道。&nbsp;<br />\n據英國研究，82.5%肥婆都唔會剃腳毛，因為烏低身嗰下等於做sit up，有違肥人忠旨。&nbsp;<br />\n所以肥婆啲腳毛永遠好似鐵線咁粗。&nbsp;<br />\n奶西嘅時候叫佢瞓低你忠個頭埋去，兩隻手要掃佢隻腳啲鐵線等佢起雞皮，然後叫佢嗰對火腿夾實自己個頭唔好比空氣流出。&nbsp;<br />\n陣咸魚味喺真空環境會得到昇華，係有層次而漸進的。<br />\n奶嗰時攝攝聲，有3D立體音響加回音效果。&nbsp;<br />\n你嗅覺，味覺，觸覺，聽覺得到前所未有嘅享受，呢啲先叫人生啊。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n啪啪啪嗰part唔多講，因為肥婆塊田多肉好撞係常識，你塞咗入去會感受到溫暖同安全感，比一層一層肉緊緊包住。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n成日笑肥婆以為自己好識食嗰啲人，根本就係未夠班，自以為是嘅表現。你比食女界嘅高手揀減肥前欣宜定係整容後楊怡，佢完全唔想答你，一嚟佢唔想笑勁你問無聊野，二嚟佢已經諗緊點班支美極返嚟。"},{"pid":"cbbd9f9292df51ad58c5c1e205d519fdc69ca0b6","tid":227352,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T07:35:06.000Z","msg":"睇埋男果個，竟然冇問介唔介紹女朋友係唔係處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a635c75396ffab90b47341d335b140fcb268805c","tid":227352,"uid":107983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T07:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇埋男果個，竟然冇問介唔介紹女朋友係唔係處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問嚟有春用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實答介意<br />\n真係拍拖邊個會介意依啲嘢，咪又係照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62b840b62d27781d689551bb49041dc364203a8","tid":227352,"uid":107983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T07:45:36.000Z","msg":"補返圖先<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xh52s3tj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxh52s3tj&h=d6deca84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xw3e69dp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxw3e69dp&h=c46eca75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vs62rcz8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvs62rcz8&h=16a6dd53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/i1obyq0l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fi1obyq0l&h=2005115f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74dd5022cc57b1280e26505590b1c83fdf6896d7","tid":227352,"uid":35653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T07:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個肥婆 <span style=\"color: red;\">我屌佢</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\